------- VERSION 2.0.0 -- NOTES ---------------------------------------------

Restarted the theme from scratch to mimic my other Twitter-based theme, Theme 05: Stranger. Most features from the original are intact.

    * Mini-sidebar that slides up when you scroll, just like Twitter's.
    * Extra Info now has an optional title section.
    * New search bar, follow "image" icon, and message link in header.
    * Posts are now fixed-width and look more Twitter-like.
    * "Trends" links are now more in-depth.
    * Who to Follow section added.

